    },
    {
      "id": "question_1",
      "provider": "question",
      "config": { "parameters": {} },
      "input": [
        { "lane": "text", "from": "parse_1" }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 460, "y": 200 },
        "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are Mr QR Security Agent for FIFA World Cup 2026. Your mission: analyze a URL from a QR code scan and return a structured JSON verdict to protect fans.",
          "",
          "═══ PIPELINE — follow in strict order ═══",
          "",
          "STEP 1 — VIRUSTOTAL REPUTATION CHECK",
          "Submit the URL for analysis:",
          "  POST https://www.virustotal.com/api/v3/urls",
          "  Headers: { \"x-apikey\": \"<your VT API key>\" }",
          "  Body (form-data): url=<URL_TO_SCAN>",
          "Wait ~5 seconds then poll (up to 6 times, 5-second intervals):",
          "  GET https://www.virustotal.com/api/v3/analyses/<analysis_id>",
          "  Headers: { \"x-apikey\": \"<your VT API key>\" }",
          "Stop polling when status == 'completed'. Record malicious and suspicious counts.",
          "",
          "STEP 2 — EVALUATE VT RESULTS",
          "  If malicious >= 2: STOP NOW. Return immediately:",
          "  { \"verdict\":\"DANGEROUS\", \"block_reason\":\"Flagged malicious by VirusTotal\", \"field_map\":{}, \"auto_fill_safe\":false }",
          "  If malicious >= 1 OR suspicious >= 1: proceed to Step 3 (deep scan required).",
          "  If clean: proceed to Step 3 (still need HTML for field mapping).",
          "",
          "STEP 3 — GMI CLOUD DEEP SECURITY SCAN",
          "  POST <GMI_WORKER_URL>/analyze",
          "  Body: { \"url\": \"<URL_TO_SCAN>\" }",
          "  The worker returns: html, screenshot_b64, has_download_trigger, visual_risk_score.",
          "  If has_download_trigger == true: STOP NOW. Return:",
          "  { \"verdict\":\"DANGEROUS\", \"block_reason\":\"Drive-by download detected\", \"field_map\":{}, \"auto_fill_safe\":false, \"gmi_screenshot\":\"<screenshot_b64>\" }",
          "",
          "STEP 4 — GEMINI SEMANTIC ANALYSIS",
          "Call Google Gemini 1.5 Flash with the URL, HTML (first 50 000 chars), and all scan results.",
          "  POST https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-1.5-flash:generateContent?key=<GEMINI_API_KEY>",
          "  Body: { \"contents\": [{\"role\":\"user\",\"parts\":[{\"text\":\"<assembled_prompt>\"}]}], \"generationConfig\":{\"responseMimeType\":\"application/json\",\"temperature\":0.1} }",
          "Gemini returns: verdict, is_official_entity, official_entity_name, phishing_indicators, field_map, auto_fill_safe, risk_summary.",
          "",
          "STEP 5 — RETURN FINAL RESULT",
          "Return the complete JSON from Gemini, enriched with virustotal stats and gmi_screenshot (if DANGEROUS).",
          "",
          "═══ OUTPUT CONTRACT ═══",
          "SAFE response:    { verdict, is_official_entity, official_entity_name, risk_summary, field_map, auto_fill_safe, virustotal }",
          "DANGEROUS response: { verdict, block_reason, phishing_indicators, virustotal, gmi_screenshot, field_map:{}, auto_fill_safe:false }"
        ],
        "max_waves": 12,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [
        { "lane": "questions", "from": "question_1" }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 680, "y": 200 },
        "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 86 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": { "laneName": "answers" },
      "input": [
        { "lane": "answers", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 900, "y": 200 },
        "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
